description: Italians have been shocked by the death of a 43-year-old DJ, who disappeared with her son.
title: Italy Viviana Parisi death: Child's remains found in mystery search
title_page: Italy Viviana Parisi death: Child's remains found in mystery search - BBC News
maintext: Parisi was seen climbing over the guard rail beside the road and walking away. One witness described her as "extremely agitated", Ansa news agency reported. The family eventually told police that she had been carrying Gioele in her arms and he was unhurt.
